retry.description:
The component **{component_name}** (domain: {component}) was not installed correctly (installed version "{installed_version}" instead of "{desired_version}")

You can retry by pressing the "Submit" button.

You can find the release files here: {release}

abort.install_error:
There were problems retrying the installation.

Manually check the component folder (config/custom_components/{component}) before proceeding with the restart.

You can find the release files here: {release}
